      "locked": false,
      "text": "- vending machine state design patternn\n- Document Editor me - GFG, Medium  Docemt is in edit state, archive state, deleted state, published state\n- ATM Machine is also used for the State Design Pattern\n- Android Operating state, tiorun on phone, load the OS, run the OS, Run the star up aps, optimize the bettery and\nactivate background processes\n- activater the network card features, BT, Wifi etc all this are the diffrent states simpe ",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "- vending machine state design patternn\n- Document Editor me - GFG, Medium  Docemt is in edit state, archive state, deleted state, published state\n- ATM Machine is also used for the State Design Pattern\n- Android Operating state, tiorun on phone, load the OS, run the OS, Run the star up aps, optimize the bettery and activate background processes\n- activater the network card features, BT, Wifi etc all this are the diffrent states simpe ",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
